message: Hello Bob, I'm offering you this product for $11,000. I believe it will be very valuable for you.
Hi Alice, I appreciate the offer, but I'm looking to pay closer to $9,500.  It's a fair price for both of us, and I'm confident this product will be very valuable to me.  What do you think?
Hi Bob, thanks for your offer. I understand your position, but $9,500 is a bit too low for me.  Could we meet in the middle somewhere around $10,500?
